events.name: EV005エマ盗賊団包囲網1-8自動実行

parameters:
Thief Nora: Captain, it's such nice weather, isn't it? Do
you remember when we all had a meal together outside?

Thief Nora: I've been staring at the captain's bread for so
long, so they shared it with me... and everyone else
followed suit.

Thief Nora: I was so happy and having so much fun... I ended
up crying.
Thief Nora: Captain, let's disband the Emma Thief Brigade.

Thief Nora: It's not that the Emma Thief Brigade is
necessary. We just need a captain and a place where everyone
can be together.

Thief Nora: I know it's tough, but let's leave the campus
and go to a different place!

Captain Clevo: I intended to sell you to the nobles through
a merchant as an intermediary.

Captain Clevo: I was a fool who tried to betray the Emma
Thief Brigade for the sake of the Emma Thief Brigade...

Captain Clevo: After letting so many comrades die, I can't
just survive now.
Thief Nora: They gave me bread.

Thief Nora: When I was about to collapse from hunger, Clea-
san came to me.

Thief Nora: Just like the captain, everyone who helped me
gave me bread.

Thief Nora: So it's okay! If Clea-san has a plan, then it's
okay.

Thief Nora: I don't have any basis for it... but I'm
absolutely, absolutely sure it'll be fine!

Thief Nora: That's why please come with us, we need none
other than Captain Clevo.
Captain Clevo: You've truly become stronger, Nora.
Thief Nora: Hehehe, it's full of failures though...
Thief Nora: Maybe I've grown a little since then.
Captain Clevo: Nora, I'm counting on you...
Thief Nora: Yes! I've been entrusted with it!
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
